OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore than 20 councils      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmoving to cashless parking 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 20 councils across England   
OL,6, are removing pay and display parking   
OL,7, machines and asking people to pay using
OL,8, an app instead.                        
OL,10,FEight councils - all in London - have  
OL,11,Falready removed all their machines,    
OL,12,Fwhile 14 have removed some.            
OL,14,FCouncils say this saves money by       
OL,15,Freducing the risk of theft and avoiding
OL,16,Fthe need to upgrade machines.          
OL,18,FBut charities say the changes are      
OL,19,F"disastrous" for people without a      
OL,20,Fsmartphone, especially the elderly.    
